            <li><a href="https://kidaflow.com/contact" class="nav-link highlight" target="_blank">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mobile-menu-btn">☰</div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content-center">
                <span class="hero-label">ABOUT KIDAFLOW</span>
                <h1>Building AI Systems That Actually Work</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">A Kenyan AI automation agency delivering production-ready systems for growing
                    businesses worldwide</p>

                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Automations Delivered</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Clients Served</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">4.97/5</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Client Rating</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">4</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Continents</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do Section (Merged Services + Approach) -->
    <section class="services-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
            <div class="services-list">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">01</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>AI Voice Agents</h3>
                        <p>Custom voice agents using Retell AI, Vapi, and ElevenLabs for 24/7 customer engagement</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">02</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>CRM Automation</h3>
                        <p>GoHighLevel, ServiceTitan, and Salesforce workflow automation and integration</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">03</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Workflow Orchestration</h3>
                        <p>Complex automation systems using n8n, Make, and Zapier</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">04</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Document Processing & OCR</h3>
                        <p>Intelligent document processing for data extraction and automation</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">05</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Custom API Integrations</h3>
                        <p>Seamless connections between your business tools and systems</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">06</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Operations Automation</h3>
                        <p>Automate data processing and workflows for accounting, finance, law firms, and service
                            businesses</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">07</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Custom Solutions</h3>
                        <p>Build automation solutions tailored to each company's tools, processes, and growth goals</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-number">08</div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>AI-Powered Systems</h3>
                        <p>Design and implement AI systems for CRM, sales automation, booking, and lead management</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>

            <div class="story-content">
                <div class="story-intro">
                    <p class="story-highlight">In March 2025, two 25-year-old founders in Nairobi, Kenya launched
                        KiDaFlow. No investors. No roadmap. No clients. Just a shared obsession with building systems
                        that actually work and grow businesses.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="story-body">
                    <p>Randy Kipkurui came from a tech background, David from engineering, and both were mind-blown by
                        what AI could do for real businesses.</p>

                    <p>They watched local companies juggle leads across WhatsApp, email, and spreadsheets—losing money
                        every day to manual chaos. The opportunity was obvious: bring world-class automation to growing
                        businesses that couldn't afford to keep hiring their way out of operational bottlenecks.</p>

                    <div class="milestone-box">
                        <p><strong>Since launch,</strong> the team has built over <strong>500 automations</strong>
                            across AI agents, document processing systems, CRMs, and data workflows for more than
                            <strong>15 international businesses</strong>.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <p>They've partnered with startups, agencies, home services companies, accounting firms, law
                        practices, and real estate investors across four continents.</p>

                    <p class="story-lesson"><em>The hard lesson learned early: Every great system starts with one manual
                            process done really well—then you scale what works.</em></p>

                    <p>It hasn't been easy. There have been late nights, lost leads, and rebuilds that took twice as
                        long as planned. But every system taught the team something new about clarity, scale, and what
                        real impact looks like when you move beyond features and focus on outcomes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who We Are Section -->
    <section class="team-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>

            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="member-avatar">RK</div>
                    <h3>Randy Kipkurui</h3>
                    <p class="member-role">Co-Founder</p>
                    <p class="member-bio">Tech background with expertise in AI automation and system architecture</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="member-avatar">DM</div>
                    <h3>David</h3>
                    <p class="member-role">Co-Founder</p>
                    <p class="member-bio">Engineering background focused on workflow optimization and integration</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-description">
                <p><strong>KiDaFlow Group</strong> is a performance and ROI-focused AI automation partner for growing
                    businesses.</p>
                <p>Based in <strong>Nairobi, Kenya</strong>, and serving clients internationally across multiple
                    industries.</p>
                <p>We combine deep technical skills in automation and AI with hands-on business experience implementing
                    systems inside real companies.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How We Work Section -->
    <section class="how-we-work-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">How We Work</h2>

            <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="process-step">
                    <h3>Clear Discovery</h3>
                    <p>Start with clear discovery: where time, money, and leads are being lost today.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="process-step">
                    <h3>Fast Results</h3>
                    <p>Launch focused automation projects that show fast results, then scale what works.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="process-step">
                    <h3>Measure Everything</h3>
                    <p>Measure everything against concrete metrics like hours saved, leads recovered, and revenue
                        impact.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Believe Section -->
    <section class="beliefs-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What We Believe</h2>

            <div class="beliefs-grid">
                <div class="belief-card">
                    <h3>Performance Over Hype</h3>
                    <p>AI should be judged by performance, not hype or features.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="belief-card">
                    <h3>Transparency Matters</h3>
                    <p>Automation must be transparent and understandable for founders and teams.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="belief-card">
                    <h3>Simple Goal</h3>
                    <p>Help businesses scale without adding headcount by turning messy, manual work into clean,
                        automated systems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section fade-in-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2>Ready to Automate Your Business?</h2>
                <p>Let's build systems that drive real results for your growing business</p>
                <a href="https://kidaflow.com/contact" class="btn-cta">Schedule a Free Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
